# Build stage
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

# Copy dependency files first for better caching
COPY pom.xml ./
RUN mvn dependency:go-offline -B

# Copy source and build
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests -B && mv target/*.jar app.jar

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL org.opencontainers.image.title="Java Analytics Dashboard"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Production-ready analytics dashboard"

# Install dependencies: curl for healthcheck, font packages for PDF generation
RUN apk update && apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    font-noto-cjk \
    && rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

WORKDIR /app

# Create non-root user
RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

# Import AWS RDS root CA certificate
RUN curl -fsSL https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem > /tmp/rds-ca.pem && \
    keytool -import -trustcacerts -alias rds-root-ca -file /tmp/rds-ca.pem \
        -keystore /opt/java/openjdk/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca.pem

# Import Azure DigiCert root certificate
RUN curl -fsSL https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt.pem > /tmp/azure-ca.pem && \
    keytool -import -trustcacerts -alias azure-digicert -file /tmp/azure-ca.pem \
        -keystore /opt/java/openjdk/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/azure-ca.pem

# Copy JAR from builder
COPY --from=builder /build/app.jar ./app.jar

# Set permissions
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
